// query drafts derived from policy/questions.md per
// skills/factlog/references/text-to-datalog.md
// Only facts/accepted.dl entities/relations are used; multi-word
// entities are quoted. At least one query resolves against the
// accepted facts so the logic_report.txt "Query evaluation" section
// is populated (this is the AC3 demonstration).

// q1: What is Claude Code and who developed it?
relation("Claude Code", "developed_by", "Anthropic")?

// q2: What tools or capabilities does Claude Code use?
relation("Claude Code", "uses", "Claude model family")?

// q3: What is the factlog plugin and what does it do?
relation("factlog", "is_a", "Claude Code plugin")?

// q4: Which factlog steps are performed by Claude vs deterministic scripts?
// The split (Claude vs scripts) is not an accepted relation in this KB,
// so the question is routed to human review rather than a Datalog query.
review_required("Which steps in factlog are performed by Claude and which by deterministic scripts?")?
